OL,3,COne-off #150 energy bills discount -
OL,4,Cwho is eligible and how does it work?
OL,6,FMore than six million households
OL,7,Facross England, Scotland and Wales
OL,8,Fwill now receive some form of help.
OL,10,FPeople in England and Wales will
OL,11,Fqualify for the Warm Home Discount
OL,12,Fthis winter if they are receiving one
OL,13,Fof the following means-tested benefits
OL,14,Fand are named on the electricity bill,
OL,15,Feither in their own name, that of
OL,16,Ftheir partner, or their legal
OL,17,Frepresentative.
