OL,3,COne-off #150 energy bills discount -
OL,4,Cwho is eligible and how does it work?
OL,6,FIf you live in Scotland, the same
OL,7,Fcriteria apply, but you must also meet
OL,8,Fthe criteria set out by your specific
OL,9,Fenergy supplier.
OL,11,FHow do you know if you are eligible?
OL,13,FThe letters are being sent to
OL,14,Fhouseholds across England and Wales
OL,15,Ffrom Tuesday.
OL,17,FAround 250,000 eligible households
OL,18,Fwill be notified this week, and every
OL,19,Fhousehold entitled to the discount
OL,20,Fshould receive a letter before January.
