OL,3,COne-off #150 energy bills discount -
OL,4,Cwho is eligible and how does it work?
OL,6,FIf you do not get a letter but think
OL,7,Fyou are eligible, you must contact the
OL,8,FWarm Home Discount Scheme by February
OL,9,F28, 2026.
OL,11,FHow does it work?
OL,13,FFor the vast majority of recipients,
OL,14,F#150 will be automatically deducted
OL,15,Ffrom their energy bill without them
OL,16,Fneeding to take any action.
