OL,3,COne-off #150 energy bills discount -
OL,4,Cwho is eligible and how does it work?
OL,6,FThe Warm Home Discount Scheme has
OL,7,Fexisted in various forms since April
OL,8,F2011, and was introduced to help low-
OL,9,Fincome and vulnerable households heat
OL,10,Ftheir homes in the winter months.
OL,12,FKeir Starmer has said the cash
OL,13,Finjection "will help people manage
OL,14,Ftheir bills while (the government
OL,15,Ffixes) the rusting energy system we
OL,16,Finherited".
