OL,3,COne-off #150 energy bills discount -
OL,4,Cwho is eligible and how does it work?
OL,6,F"Because it is only through our clean
OL,7,Fenergy mission that we will get bills
OL,8,Fdown for everyone in the long run,
OL,9,Fcreating jobs and economic growth
OL,10,Falong the way."
OL,12,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said he
OL,13,Fis "determined to tackle energy
OL,14,Faffordability for families, and this
OL,15,Fwinter more people will be helped as a
OL,16,Fresult".
